<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en"><head><meta charset="utf-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1"><title>Edit Academy</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css"><link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/navbar.css">
<style>
body{margin:0;background:#f5f8ff;font-family:Poppins,Segoe UI,Arial,sans-serif;color:#0f172a}*{box-sizing:border-box}.main{padding:20px 26px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px}.hero,.row{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:16px;align-items:flex-start;flex-wrap:wrap}.title{font-size:24px;font-weight:800;color:#083454}.subtitle{font-size:13px;color:#64748b;max-width:960px;line-height:1.7}.card{background:#fff;border:1px solid #e4ecfb;border-radius:18px;padding:18px;box-shadow:0 10px 26px rgba(12,38,73,.06)}.grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,minmax(0,1fr));gap:14px}.compact-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,minmax(0,1fr))}.full{grid-column:1/-1}.group{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:7px}label{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#334155}input,select,textarea{width:100%;border:1px solid #dbe3f6;border-radius:12px;padding:11px 12px;background:#fff;font:inherit}textarea{min-height:100px}.btn{padding:11px 15px;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid #dbe3f6;background:#eef4ff;color:#0a3d62;text-decoration:none;font-weight:700;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;cursor:pointer}.btn.primary{background:#0a3d62;color:#fff;border-color:#0a3d62}.btn.danger{background:#fff1f2;color:#b91c1c;border-color:#fecdd3}.btn[disabled]{opacity:.45;cursor:not-allowed}.icon-btn{padding:10px 12px}.section-title{font-size:14px;font-weight:800;color:#0a3d62;margin:0 0 12px}.help{font-size:12px;color:#6b7280;line-height:1.6}.alert{padding:12px 14px;border-radius:12px;background:#fff1f2;color:#991b1b;border:1px solid #fecdd3}.tip,.inline-note{padding:14px;border-radius:14px;background:#f8fbff;border:1px solid #dbe7ff;color:#33506b;font-size:13px;line-height:1.7}.inline-note{margin-top:14px;padding:10px 12px;display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:flex-start}.stack{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px}.actions,.toolbar,.section-actions,.section-add-bar,.level-card-top{display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center}.campus-card,.level-card{border:1px solid #dbe7ff;border-radius:16px;background:#fbfdff}.campus-head{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:12px;align-items:center;padding:14px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid #edf3ff}.campus-toggle{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:12px;background:transparent;border:none;padding:0;cursor:pointer;text-align:left;color:inherit;font:inherit;flex:1}.campus-title,.level-title{font-weight:800;color:#0a3d62}.campus-toggle-icon{width:26px;height:26px;border-radius:999px;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:#eef4ff;color:#0a3d62;flex:0 0 26px}.muted{font-size:12px;color:#64748b}.block{display:block;margin-top:4px}.panel{padding:16px;display:none}.panel.open{display:block}.levels-wrap{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;margin-top:14px}.level-card{padding:14px}.section-row{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:10px;align-items:center;padding:10px 12px;border:1px solid #dbe7ff;border-radius:12px;background:#fff}.section-name{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#184069;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}.sections-stack{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;margin-top:10px}.empty{padding:16px;border:1px dashed #cbd5e1;border-radius:14px;color:#64748b;background:#f8fafc}.empty.compact{padding:12px}.hidden{display:none!important}.toast{position:fixed;right:18px;bottom:18px;padding:12px 16px;border-radius:12px;background:#0a3d62;color:#fff;box-shadow:0 12px 28px rgba(0,0,0,.18);opacity:0;transform:translateY(12px);pointer-events:none;transition:.18s ease}.toast.show{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}@media (max-width:980px){.grid,.compact-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.main{padding:16px}.campus-head{align-items:flex-start;flex-direction:column}.section-row{align-items:flex-start;flex-direction:column}.section-actions,.section-add-bar,.level-card-top{width:100%}}
</style>
</head>
<body><%- include('./navbar') %><main class="main"><div class="hero"><div><div class="title">Edit Academy / Tenant</div><div class="subtitle">Keep school units independent, with campuses, levels and sections nested cleanly under the tenant. Use this as the fixed base architecture for all later academic modules.</div></div><a href="/super-admin/schools/<%= tenant._id %>" class="btn"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-left"></i> Back</a></div>
<% if (error) { %><div class="alert"><%= error %></div><% } %>
<% const initialSchoolUnits = (((tenant || {}).settings || {}).academics || {}).schoolUnits || []; %>
<form action="/super-admin/schools/<%= tenant._id %>/edit" method="POST" class="stack"><div class="card"><div class="section-title">Identity & Access</div><div class="grid"><div class="group"><label>Academy / Tenant Name</label><input name="name" value="<%= tenant?.name || '' %>" required></div><div class="group"><label>Tenant Code</label><input value="<%= tenant?.code || '' %>" disabled></div><div class="group"><label>Country</label><input name="country" value="<%= tenant?.country || '' %>"></div><div class="group"><label>Custom Domain</label><input name="customDomain" value="<%= tenant?.customDomain || '' %>" placeholder="academy.example.com"></div><div class="group"><label>Timezone</label><input name="timezone" value="<%= tenant?.timezone || 'Africa/Kampala' %>"></div><div class="group"><label>Currency</label><input name="currency" value="<%= tenant?.currency || 'USD' %>"></div></div></div>
<div class="card"><div class="row"><div><div class="section-title" style="margin-bottom:6px">School Units, Campuses, Levels & Sections</div><div class="help">School units own the public profile. Campuses own operations. Levels and sections stay under the selected school unit and become the base for subjects, students, staff, timetables and exams.</div></div><button type="button" class="btn primary" id="addSchoolUnitBtn"><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i> Add School Unit</button></div><input type="hidden" name="schoolUnitsJson" id="schoolUnitsJson"><div id="campusList" class="stack" style="margin-top:14px" data-campus-builder-root="1" data-hidden-input-id="schoolUnitsJson" data-add-btn-id="addSchoolUnitBtn" data-initial-data-id="campusBuilderData" data-draft-key="classic-academy-edit-<%= tenant._id %>"></div></div>
<div class="card"><div class="section-title">Admin / Owner</div><div class="grid"><div class="group"><label>Owner Name</label><input name="ownerName" value="<%= tenant?.ownerName || '' %>" required></div><div class="group"><label>Owner Email</label><input type="email" name="ownerEmail" value="<%= tenant?.ownerEmail || '' %>" required></div><div class="group"><label>Owner Phone</label><input name="ownerPhone" value="<%= tenant?.ownerPhone || '' %>"></div><div class="group"><label>Status</label><select name="status"><% ['trial','active','suspended','cancelled'].forEach(function(s){ %><option value="<%= s %>" <%= (tenant?.status || 'trial')===s?'selected':'' %>><%= s.charAt(0).toUpperCase()+s.slice(1) %></option><% }) %></select></div></div></div>
<div class="card"><div class="section-title">Plan & Profile</div><div class="grid"><div class="group"><label>Plan</label><select name="planId" required><option value="">Select plan</option><% (plans || []).forEach(function(plan){ %><option value="<%= plan._id %>" <%= String(tenant?.planId?._id || tenant?.planId || '')===String(plan._id)?'selected':'' %>><%= plan.name %></option><% }) %></select></div><div class="group"><label>Profile Enabled</label><select name="profileEnabled"><option value="true" <%= (((tenant.settings||{}).profile||{}).enabled !== false)?'selected':'' %>>Active</option><option value="false" <%= (((tenant.settings||{}).profile||{}).enabled === false)?'selected':'' %>>Inactive</option></select></div><div class="group"><label>Profile Verified</label><select name="profileVerified"><option value="true" <%= (((tenant.settings||{}).profile||{}).verified === true)?'selected':'' %>>Verified</option><option value="false" <%= (((tenant.settings||{}).profile||{}).verified !== true)?'selected':'' %>>Not Verified</option></select></div></div><div class="tip" style="margin-top:16px">Tenant login stays one. School unit profiles live under the tenant, while campuses handle operational scope and later subject, student, staff, timetable and exam ownership.</div><div class="actions" style="margin-top:16px"><button type="submit" class="btn primary"><i class="fa-solid fa-floppy-disk"></i> Save Changes</button></div></div>
</form></main><div id="campusBuilderToast" class="toast"></div><script id="campusBuilderData" type="application/json"><%- JSON.stringify(initialSchoolUnits) %></script><script src="/js/campus-structure-builder.js"></script><script src="/js/navbar.js"></script></body></html>
